OL,3,CInheritance tax reforms having
OL,4,C'chilling effect' on Scottish farming
OL,5,C` Swinney
OL,7,FInheritance tax reforms introduced in
OL,8,Fthe Chancellor's Autumn Budget are
OL,9,Falready having a "chilling effect" on
OL,10,Ffarming and rural businesses in
OL,11,FScotland, John Swinney has said.
OL,13,FSpeaking ahead of an address at the
OL,14,FAgriScot conference in Edinburgh on
OL,15,FWednesday, the First Minister said the
OL,16,Fdecision to remove some inheritance
OL,17,Ftax relief from farms was causing
OL,18,F"unacceptable levels of stress" among
OL,19,Ffarmers.
