OL,5,C` Swinney
OL,7,FUnder plans announced in the Budget,
OL,8,Finheritance tax will be charged at 20%
OL,9,Fon agricultural assets above #1
OL,10,Fmillion, although Chancellor Rachel
OL,11,FReeves has said that in some cases the
OL,12,Fthreshold could in practice be about
OL,13,F#3 million.
