OL,7,FMr Swinney said it was "deeply
OL,8,Fdisappointing" that the Scottish
OL,9,FGovernment was not consulted on the
OL,10,Fchange, and he called on the UK
OL,11,FGovernment to "urgently" commit to
OL,12,Fpublishing impact assessments of the
OL,13,Fproposals on farmers and crofters in
OL,14,FScotland.
