OL,3,CInheritance tax reforms having
OL,4,C'chilling effect' on Scottish farming
OL,5,C` Swinney
OL,7,F"The UK Budget could scarcely have
OL,8,Fbeen more indifferent to the needs of
OL,9,Frural communities and the rural
OL,10,Feconomy, on top of a lack of certainty
OL,11,Fover long-term funding, which we would
OL,12,Fhave through membership of the EU,
OL,13,Fmeaning we now have an inadequate
OL,14,Fsettlement.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
