PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F307A1731467714
OL,3,CInheritance tax reforms having
OL,4,C'chilling effect' on Scottish farming
OL,5,C` Swinney
OL,7,F"I know this is already having a
OL,8,Fchilling effect on farming and rural
OL,9,Fbusinesses. The UK Government must
OL,10,Furgently commit to undertake and
OL,11,Fpublish impact assessments on its
OL,12,Fbudget proposals on farmers and
OL,13,Fcrofters in Scotland.
OL,15,F"Fundamentally, the Scottish
OL,16,FGovernment wants to see a tax system
OL,17,Fthat supports rather than hinders
OL,18,Forderly succession planning and the
OL,19,Ftransfer of land to the next
OL,20,Fgeneration of custodians.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
