PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F307A1731467714
OL,3,CInheritance tax reforms having
OL,4,C'chilling effect' on Scottish farming
OL,5,C` Swinney
OL,7,F"No matter whether or not a
OL,8,Fsignificant number of businesses are
OL,9,Faffected directly, it is deeply
OL,10,Fdisappointing that the Chancellor
OL,11,Fchose not to work with the Scottish
OL,12,FGovernment before acting on this
OL,13,Fsensitive matter.
OL,15,F"The UK Government must also provide
OL,16,Fclarity on the future of financial
OL,17,Fsupport for the sector, after
OL,18,Fconfirming in the Autumn Budget that
OL,19,Fagricultural funding will be baselined.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
