OL,3,CInheritance tax reforms having
OL,4,C'chilling effect' on Scottish farming
OL,5,C` Swinney
OL,7,F"Any move to break the link between
OL,8,Fland area farmed and funding increases
OL,9,Fin Scotland ignores our ongoing
OL,10,Fcommitment to active farming and food
OL,11,Fproduction, and could constrain our
OL,12,Fefforts to transform our industry for
OL,13,Fthe future."
OL,15,FA UK Government spokesperson said:
OL,16,F"This budget took the difficult
OL,17,Fdecisions to fix the public services
OL,18,Fcrumbling across the United Kingdom,
OL,19,Fincluding Scotland, and address the
OL,20,F#22 billion fiscal black hole
OL,21,Finherited from the previous government.
