OL,3,CInheritance tax reforms having
OL,4,C'chilling effect' on Scottish farming
OL,5,C` Swinney
OL,7,F"With 40% of agricultural property
OL,8,Frelief going to the 7% of wealthiest
OL,9,Fclaimants, we made the decision to
OL,10,Fensure the relief is fiscally
OL,11,Fsustainable.
OL,13,F"Around 500 claims each year will be
OL,14,Fimpacted and farm-owning couples can
OL,15,Fpass on up to #3 million without
OL,16,Fpaying any inheritance tax ` this is a
OL,17,Ffair and balanced approach."
